C o e X I s T

flowRoot.flowPara: Many rich people can easily free themselves even for murder and rape with money. They simply buy the judge that wears a price tag instead of morality and honour...

The usual rhetorical automatism would be "Everyone has his price" even Judges are for sale. We think "Everyone" is a rumor, but many young people do not realize, that their wages actually are paid by Satan (for example from the Army). Not informed by the company, that many people had to die in the name of the employer, and if the young employee would ask relevant questions the company would fire him.
Behavioural "Sciences" = to boss people around instead of educating them for "efficiency". The resulting late sequelae are then to be payed by the community if they can be fixed at all...

The brain automatically tells: pain (injuries) is bad, so the brain will try to save the pony from situations where it feels pain again, so the scene will be burned in the brain and in the future automatically avoided (avoidance behavior)
Physical violence against children is prohibited by law but in Switzerland but unfortunately still very common.
